      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">stanza</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·邶風·012.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Maou-Vewt.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>何其處也，必有與也，何其久也，必有以也。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Why do they rest without stirring?
It must be they expect allies.
Why do they prolong the time?
There must be a reason for their conduct.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-beifeng-012__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
